  <h1>Delete Your <span class="app-name">Pawket</span> Account</h1>
  
  <p>This page explains how to delete your Pawket account and what data will be removed.</p>

  <h2>How to Delete Your Account</h2>
  <p>You can delete your account directly within the Pawket app by following these steps:</p>
  <ol>
    <li>Open the <strong>Pawket</strong> app on your device</li>
    <li>Tap the <strong>Menu icon</strong> (☰) in the top navigation</li>
    <li>Select <strong>"Profile"</strong> from the menu options</li>
    <li>Scroll down to the bottom of the Profile section</li>
    <li>Tap the <strong>"DELETE ACCOUNT"</strong> button (shown in red)</li>
    <li>Review the deletion warning and tap <strong>"Delete Forever"</strong> to confirm</li>
  </ol>

  <div class="warning-box">
    <p><strong>⚠️ Warning:</strong> Account deletion is permanent and cannot be undone. All your data will be immediately and permanently deleted.</p>
  </div>

  <h2>Data That Will Be Deleted</h2>
  <p>When you delete your account, the following data will be permanently removed:</p>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Profile Information</strong> – Your name, email address, and account preferences</li>
    <li><strong>Financial Transactions</strong> – All income and expense records you've entered</li>
    <li><strong>Daily Goals</strong> – Your bite-sized goals and completion history</li>
    <li><strong>Financial Goals</strong> – Any savings goals or financial targets you've set</li>
    <li><strong>Pet Data</strong> – Your virtual pet's mood, status, and interaction history</li>
    <li><strong>Streaks & Achievements</strong> – Your app usage streaks and earned achievements</li>
    <li><strong>Notification Preferences</strong> – Your notification settings and FCM tokens</li>
    <li><strong>Subscription Information</strong> – Your subscription status and billing records</li>
    <li><strong>In-App Notifications</strong> – Any notifications sent to your account</li>
    <li><strong>Challenge Progress</strong> – Any active or completed challenges</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Data Retention Period</h2>
  <div class="info-box">
    <p><strong>No retention period:</strong> All data is deleted immediately upon account deletion. Pawket does not retain any user data after deletion is confirmed.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="contact-section">
    <h2>Need Help?</h2>
    <p>If you are unable to access the app or need assistance with account deletion, you can request deletion by contacting us:</p>
    <p><strong>Email:</strong> <a href="mailto:support@pawketfinance.com">support@pawketfinance.com</a></p>
    <p>Please include the email address associated with your Pawket account in your request. We will process your deletion request within 30 days.</p>
  </div>

